optional_parameters.description:
Get **facets** filter values from **api/v1/getProductList** endpoint.
Note: **id** in **facets** should be key and **id** in **facetValues** should be array of filter.
Example: { 'range' : ['new_season'] , 'attribute_10155' : ['6764' , '7699'] }

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://asos10.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/getProductListBySearchTerm"
querystring = {"priceMin": "", "facets": "", "priceMax": "", "sort": "", "languageShort": "en", "limit": "50", "currency": "USD", "store": "US", "offset": "0", "sizeSchema": "US", "country": "US", "searchTerm": "Tomm"}

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "asos10.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, params=querystring)
print(response.json())

